\n<br />\n2003年的SARS被認為源於有人食用野生動物果子狸，涉事兒童圖書《動物小百科》內有關果子狸的介紹文章，不但稱果子狸可食用，更形容果子狸是中國歷史悠久的稀有「山珍」，「它（牠）們的脂肪是化妝品生產中難得的高級原料，也可以醫治燙傷，它（牠）們的皮毛可做皮手套，它（牠）們的尾毛和針毛，可以製成毛刷和畫筆」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民批評文章內容低質，希望吃野味的習慣能在新一代的教育中逐漸消失。另有不少網民質疑文中配相並非果子狸，而是浣熊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20200212/s00004/1581479650933/%e3%80%90%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e5%85%92%e7%ab%a5%e6%9b%b8%e7%a8%b1%e3%80%8c%e6%9e%9c%e5%ad%90%e7%8b%b8%e5%8f%af%e9%a3%9f%e7%94%a8%e3%80%8d%e6%83%b9%e6%89%b9%e8%a9%95-%e5%87%ba%e7%89%88%e7%a4%be-%e5%b7%b2%e9%80%9a%e7%9f%a5%e5%85%a8%e9%9d%a2%e4%b8%8b%e6%9e%b6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20200212%2Fs00004%2F1581479650933%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e5%2585%2592%25e7%25ab%25a5%25e6%259b%25b8%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%259e%259c%25e5%25ad%2590%25e7%258b%25b8%25e5%258f%25af%25e9%25a3%259f%25e7%2594%25a8%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%2583%25b9%25e6%2589%25b9%25e8%25a9%2595-%25e5%2587%25ba%25e7%2589%2588%25e7%25a4%25be-%25e5%25b7%25b2%25e9%2580%259a%25e7%259f%25a5%25e5%2585%25a8%25e9%259d%25a2%25e4%25b8%258b%25e6%259e%25b6&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BYoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=a907d481\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20200212%2Fs00004%2F1581479650933%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e5%2585%2592%25e7%25ab%25a5%25e6%259b%25b8%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%259e%259c%25e5%25ad%2590%25e7%258b%25b8%25e5%258f%25af%25e9%25a3%259f%25e7%2594%25a8%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%2583%25b9%25e6%2589%25b9%25e8%25a9%2595-%25e5%2587%25ba%25e7%2589%2588%25e7%25a4%25be-%25e5%25b7%25b2%25e9%2580%259a%25e7%259f%25a5%25e5%2585%25a8%25e9%259d%